title: DAO PURCHASE TIMELINE
body:
We are voting on what route to take leading up to the release of $FISH.

1.) Buy 3x floor priced CCs today, skip tomorrow and buy 1 RARE with leftover ETH on 10 OCT 2021 to celebrate $FISH launch.

2.) Stick to 1 CCs a day for today and tomorrow, and buy however many we can afford on stake day.

3.) Buy an Influencer’s cat.

4.) Buy 1 a day until royalties come in.
